{"tid":1965612,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"葵芳潮食閣成功成為勵敬懲教所「私人膳食供應商」改善在囚手足伙食","createTime":"2020-04-09T14:47:32.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-09T15:45:12.000Z","uid":21470,"like":22,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"03bc318f7958674933ad345d2b83169b129dea6e","tid":1965612,"uid":21470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-09T14:47:32.000Z","msg":"潮食閣 - Yummy Corner<br />\n<br />\n特別通告，我們終於申請成功，<br />\n<br />\n成為勵敬懲教所&lt;私人膳食供應商&gt;！<br />\n<br />\n我們將於2020年4月20日開始為還押人士提供私人膳食。就算裡面只有一位手足，我們也務必提供溫暖、飽肚的膳食給她們。我們承諾必定不會讓她們肚餓。<br />\n我們特別想講，多謝邵家臻議員，梁錦威團隊及懲教署更生事務組，一直密切關注及改善在囚人士的情況，部份手足更被還押超過100天的。希望大家可以繼續關注入面手足的情況，給予多一些支持，告訴他們「我們從來沒有忘記過仼何一位」。<br />\n最後我們想講，我們也正耐心等候荔枝角收押所及壁屋懲教所的消息，我們也希望盡快成為他們的供應商。&lt;正義或許會遲到，但絕不會缺席&gt;，希望大家也要堅持下去。<br />\n#勿忘手足 #香港人加油<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/yummycornerhk/posts/3549480771735800\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fyummycornerhk%2Fposts%2F3549480771735800&d=xid8M%2BhLl0Hh6VuzhHwKVdLD3cQOkzCKckuFp%2FmPVdU%3D&h=5f44a551\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/yummycornerhk/posts/3549480771735800</a>"},{"pid":"6824374222163f3e959677ed03f33e7a9a64eddc","tid":1965612,"uid":235140,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-09T14:49:05.000Z","msg":"👍"},{"pid":"ac7229b02757c1c4232a2d84e04b8001d253049d","tid":1965612,"uid":19126,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-09T14:51:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b96957a18d0af3b134c91bb641f10b19f11fede6","tid":1965612,"uid":5378,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-09T14:51:22.000Z","msg":"良心經濟圈既龍門呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />?"},{"pid":"9bba0f6112fa7114dd60016b447be65a8d42652f","tid":1965612,"uid":268131,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-09T15:45:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n多謝邵議員"}]}